         (examples . "The following code counts the number of lines in the file somefile.txt and sets the variable ct equal to that number:\n\n(setq fil \"SOMEFILE.TXT\")\n(setq x (open fil \"r\") ct 0)\n(while (read-line x)\n  (setq ct (1+ ct))\n)\n(close x)")
