         (signature . "(initdia [dialogflag])")
         (arguments . (("dialogflag" . "Type: Integer\nA numeric value. If this argument is not present or is present and nonzero, the next use (and next use only) of a command will display that command's dialog box rather than its command line prompts.\nIf dialogflag is zero, any previous call to this function is cleared, restoring the default behavior of presenting the command line interface.")))
