                         ("screen-pt" . "Type: List\nA 2D point that specifies the X,Y location of the dialog box on the screen. The point specifies the upper-left corner of the dialog box. If you pass the point as '(-1 -1), the dialog box is opened in the default position (the center of the AutoCAD drawing area).")))
