         (guid . "GUID-4CC43BEB-3215-41AE-839B-2DCE6354241A")))
    ("repeat" .
        ((name . "repeat")
         (title . "repeat (AutoLISP)")
         (summary . "Evaluates each expression a specified number of times, and returns the value of the last expression")
         (source-kind . "AutoLISP")
         (alphabetic-group . "R")
         (feature-groups . ("Equality and Conditional"))
         (supported-platforms . "Windows and Mac OS")
         (signature . "(repeat int [expr ...])")
         (arguments . (("int" . "Type: Integer\nA numeric value. Must be a positive number.")
                         ("expr" . "Type: Integer, Real, String, List, Symbol, File, Ename (entity name), T, or nil\nOne or more atoms or expressions.")))
         (return-values . "Type: Integer, Real, String, List, Symbol, File, Ename (entity name), T, or nil\nThe value of the last expression or atom evaluated. If expr is not supplied, repeat returns nil.")
         (release-information . nil)
         (history . nil)
         (examples . "(setq a 10 b 100)\n100\n\n(repeat 4 (setq a (+ a 10)) (setq b (+ b 100)))\n500\n\nAfter evaluation, a is 50, b is 500, and repeat returns 500.\n\nIf strings are supplied as arguments, repeat returns the last string:\n\n(repeat 100 \"Me\" \"You\")\n\"You\"")
         (url . "https://help.autodesk.com/cloudhelp/2023/ENU/AutoCAD-AutoLISP-Reference/files/GUID-413F72B4-BA37-4E5E-9D51-A0091130A317.htm")
         (guid . "GUID-413F72B4-BA37-4E5E-9D51-A0091130A317")))
