         (examples . "The following code illustrates the use of vl-exit-with-error to pass a string to the *error* function of the calling namespace:\n\n(defun *error* (msg)\n  ... ; processing in VLX namespace/execution context\n(vl-exit-with-error (strcat \"My application bombed! \" msg)))")
